      "text": "7. Ta Taifna Zekſch irr lih-\ndſens/ ta Taifna Teknu fwer tu\npareiſi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "8. Ir us to Zekſu tawas Tee-\nfachanas gaidam mehs KUNGS\nus tevi/ uſ tawu Wahrdn/ un\nus tawu Beeminneschannu ſtabw\n(muhfas) Dwehfeles Eekahro-\nchana.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "9. Ar mannu Dwehfeli ilgo-\njohs es pehz tewis Naſti / ir ar\nmannu Garru/ kas eekſch man-\nnin irr/ efmu es agri nomohdā\nus tew. Jo kad tawa Sohdi-\nba wirß Semmes irr/ tad mah-\nzahs tee Eedsihwotaji tahs Pa-\nfaules Taifnibu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. Jepſchu tam Besdeewi-\ngam Schehlastiba tobp parahdi-\nta/ tomehr wiꞥſch ne mahzahs\nTaifnibu: Winsch darra Metaif-\nnibu eekſch taitnas Semmes/ jo\nwinsch ne reds ta KUNG A\nAugſtibu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. KUNGS/ tawa Rohka\nirr pa-augſtinata / to winni ne\nreds/ kad winni to redschß / tad\ntee kauneſees tahs karstas Mihle-\nſtibas Deht pahr (taweem) Lau-\ndim/ un tas Ugguns norths ta-\nwus Prettinekus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "12. KUNGS/ tu dohſt mumē\nMeeru / jo ir wiﬀus muhſus\nDarbus chi tu mums pataſſis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "13. KUNGS muhſu Deews/\n(zieti) Kungi bes tewis irr pahr\nmums waſdiſchi / tomehr zaun\ntewi ween peeminnam mehs ta-\ntwu Wahrdn.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "14. Tee irr nomirruschi un ne\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "taps dſihwi/ tee irr no Mirronu\nKahrtas/ nn ne zelſees/ tadeht\neſti tu tohs peemeklejs un iſdel-\ndejs/ un wiſſu winno Peemin-\neschannu iſnihzinajs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "15. Tu ak KUNGS! steidſees\nſtarp teen Paganeem / tu stei-\ndſees prohjam/ tu parahdi tawu\nGohdibu / tu iſplatti to tahfu\nlihds wiſſeem Pafaules Galſeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "16. KUNGS/ eekſch Beh-\ndahin tee tewis mekle / kad tu\ntohs pahrmahzi/ tad tee gauschi\nuhds.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "17. Itt ka weena apgruhti-\nnata Seetwa/ kad winnai ta\nDsemdefchana uſeet/ tad irr wiſſ-\nrat Sahpes/ un brehz fauas\nBehdas/ ta efam mehs KUNGS\npreekſch tawas Duſnibus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "18. Mehs efam apgruhtinati\nbijuſcht/ mehs efam Sahpes zee-\ntutchi/ bet mehs efam itt ka\nWehju Dsemdeifschi/ tomehr mehs\nne warraim tat Semmei palih-\ndſeht/ un tee Eedsihwotaji tahs\nPafaules ne friht femmē.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "19. Tawi Mirroni dſihwohs/\nir manna nomirruſti Meefa/ tee\nzelſees augſcham. Usinoſtsee-\ntees/ un gawitejeet juhs/ kas juhs\nPihschlōs dſihwojat/ jo ta Raffa\nirr ka taktu Sahiu Raffa/ bet to\nMirronu Semmi tu apgahſſi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "20. Etj nohſt mannu Lauschu\nPulks/ etj tawōs Kambaros/ un\naieſlehds tawas Durwis pakak\nfewim / aptieppees kahdu masa\nAzzomirkli/ kamehr ta Duſniba\npa-eet.\n"
    }
  ],
